  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375320/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1764692547\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375320/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1764692547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375320/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1764692547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375320/extras/d9cf1499fee3784d19d0d60c1b0c8f77.poster.avif?t=1764692547\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375320/extras/d9cf1499fee3784d19d0d60c1b0c8f77.webm?t=1764692547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375320/extras/d9cf1499fee3784d19d0d60c1b0c8f77.mp4?t=1764692547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You’ve been caught into trap and now you must get out of it. You don’t have any super capacity with exception to your own brain. You can only pass the room with the help of your brain, because you will have to solve the puzzle in order to open an exit. And remember - the puzzles get ever more complicated in the course of a game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Brain upgrade at every level<br></li><li>Unusual puzzles<br></li><li>Trade maps</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375320/extras/3ba9fe1339217187c25637806b1818d4.poster.avif?t=1764692547\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375320/extras/3ba9fe1339217187c25637806b1818d4.webm?t=1764692547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375320/extras/3ba9fe1339217187c25637806b1818d4.mp4?t=1764692547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375320/extras/d9cf1499fee3784d19d0d60c1b0c8f77.poster.avif?t=1764692547\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375320/extras/d9cf1499fee3784d19d0d60c1b0c8f77.webm?t=1764692547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375320/extras/d9cf1499fee3784d19d0d60c1b0c8f77.mp4?t=1764692547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You’ve been caught into trap and now you must get out of it. You don’t have any super capacity with exception to your own brain. You can only pass the room with the help of your brain, because you will have to solve the puzzle in order to open an exit. And remember - the puzzles get ever more complicated in the course of a game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Brain upgrade at every level<br></li><li>Unusual puzzles<br></li><li>Trade maps</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375320/extras/3ba9fe1339217187c25637806b1818d4.poster.avif?t=1764692547\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375320/extras/3ba9fe1339217187c25637806b1818d4.webm?t=1764692547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375320/extras/3ba9fe1339217187c25637806b1818d4.mp4?t=1764692547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
